<s> [front panel] [w3c logo] World Wide Web Consortium Web Accessibility Initiative "The power of the Web is in its universality.  </s>
<s> Access by everyone regardless of disability is an essential aspect." -- Tim Berners-Lee, W3C Director and Inventor of the World Wide Web  </s>
